title: Chapter 948 - Three Stones Of Rebirth
body:
Chapter 948 - Three Stones Of Rebirth

The world-famous lord of the City of Safe Returns carried himself humbly from beginning to end, but Su Yi nonetheless refused.

“Perhaps some other time.”

With that, he continued into the distance.

They weren’t familiar. Even if they feasted together, it would be dull.

“Brother Su, wait! We can’t let the spoils of war go to waste,” said Cui Jingyan.

It was only after she’d deftly gathered the trophies scattered across the stage that she followed Su Yi away.

Yin Xiulin made no attempt to stop them. It was only after watching Su Yi and Cui Jingyan fade from view that this mighty Profound Serenity visibly relaxed.

As if he’d been under some sort of pressure before.

“Don't just stand there. Quick, get up.” Yin Xiulin looked at the woman in black sitting on the stage.

“Yes.” Only then did she dare rise to her feet.

“Your Excellency, might I ask just who that young man was?” someone couldn’t help but ask in a low voice.

Yin Xiulin said with a complicated look on his face, “All you need to remember is that he’s the man who saved my life.”

The crowd was instantly silent.

“Ol’ Weng, are you displeased?”...
